data.description: Introducing an exceptional investment opportunity - a charming duplex with the potential to generate an impressive $29,700 in annual passive income. This property features a well-designed layout, comprising of one spacious one-bedroom unit and one comfortable two-bedroom unit. Additionally, the basement holds incredible potential, as it can be easily converted into an additional unit, transforming this property into a lucrative triplex. What sets this duplex apart is its own separate access from the back to the third unit once converted, providing privacy and convenience for all occupants. Don't miss out on this fantastic chance to secure a great investment property with promising returns.
